properties.name: Wishi
properties.short_description: YOUR PREMIUM DESTINATION FOR ONLINE STYLING
properties.description:
Wishi is an online marketplace that provides personal styling at an affordable price. It is also home to the personal stylists and provides them the opportunity to make flexible income on demand. WISHI’s stylists help users unlock their closet’s full potential while introducing them to relevant and inspiring items that are within their budget.

WISHI was named Best Startup Pitch and was founded by Lia Kislev and Clea O'hana in 2014 and has offices in San Francisco, New York, and Tel Aviv.

properties.bio:
Shay Hasson, Managing Partner WeKix.com
Shay Hasson brings more than fifteen years entrepreneurial experience leading
technology and media companies. Hasson founded the Clementina Group in the US
in 1999 with the vision of merging technology, creative and marketing disciplines to
provide uniquely integrated creative and marketing OTV application solutions. As an
entrepreneur, Hasson founded several companies including a UK-based
professional services firm, a US-based internet marketing company and an early
stage investment firm.
Hasson currently serves on the boards of clementina.net, Intr8ing.com, teewe.tv and
others.

Aya has a B.Sc. in Computer Science from Ben-Gurion University. She is an experienced technology professional in all aspects of software development with a proven record of success in architecture, design, development, QA and deployment.

properties.name: Farfetch
properties.short_description: Farfetch is an online luxury fashion retail platform.
properties.description:
Farfetch operates an e-commerce website that unites various independent fashion boutiques. It offers bags, coats, dresses, jackets, jewellery, swimwear, trouser, shoes, knitwear, suits, shorts, and accessories. 

They operate a modular end-to-end technology platform purpose built to connect the luxury fashion ecosystem worldwide. Their vision was to create a single operating system that could address the complex demands of consumers and luxury sellers alike. Their platform is built on an API-enabled proprietary technology stack, which provides the foundation for the three main components: applications, services and data. 

Farfetch serves women, men, and kids. Jose Neves founded the company in 2008, with its headquarters in London, United Kingdom.

properties.name: Seedrs
properties.short_description: Seedrs is a UK-based equity crowdfunding platform.
properties.description:
Seedrs is the leading online platform for investing in the equity of startups and other growth companies in Europe and has been named the most active investor in private companies in the UK.

Seedr allows all types of investors invest in businesses they believe in and share in their success and allow all types of growth-focused businesses raise capital and business community in the process.

The company do all of this through a simple, highly professional, online process that protects and empowers investors while helping businesses grow and generate returns
